<div class="container">
    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-lg-12">
            <h1 class="section-title-no-margin">Vlogs</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="container-90 center">
          <div class="row">
            <div class="col-4">
              <%= image_tag('nicolas_sits_left', style:"width=50px") %>
            </div>
            <div class="col-4">
              <p class="center">I've been documenting my journey in becoming a developer here in Melbourne.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="col-4">
              <%= image_tag('nicolas_sits_right', style:"width=50px") %>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="row">
            <p> Each day I'm making a short vlog about my life as a software engineer, which consists in learning new technologies at a bootcamp, concepts and attending meetups and other various interesting events, as well as helping others in their coding journey. </p>
            <p>Also, I couldn't resist the temptation to illustrate each vlog with its little doodle. Life is so much better with cartoons!</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="btn-center center">
          <% if user_signed_in? %>
          <%= link_to 'New Vlog', new_vlog_path, class: 'btn btn-outline-info btn-margin-bottom' %>
          <% end %>
        </div>
    </div>

      <section id="card-lists">
            <% @vlogs.each do |vlog| %>
            <%= render 'vlog', vlog: vlog %>
            <% end %>
      </section>

  <div class="pagination">
    <%= paginate @vlogs %>
  </div>

</div>
